<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;">主题研讨开始前，全体发展对象一同观看人民网的超燃混剪视频——五四版《骄傲的少年》。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-weight: 400; text-decoration-style: solid; text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 76, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">青春，是哪怕万人阻挡，也不曾投降的倔强；是哪怕道阻且艰，还是一往无前的无畏；是有尊严有担当，很温柔很坚强的善良……</span></strong><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-decoration-style: solid; text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">广大青年</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif; text-decoration-style: solid; text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span>用生命照亮了前进的道路，他们为中国的出路走遍全球各国，成为真正“觉醒”的中国人，如今的新时代青年也正在前辈们开拓的道路上奋勇向前。</span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;">观看完视频，各位发展对象纷纷有感而发，就“中国青年的使命与担当”这一主题开展研讨，并由小组代表发言交流感想。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEKOcBdcnTFK8G3tslKZMGAGL8LXUbFlTtTicZPgZ4nnia1RN2gdV81V1y6pCMSzy74BibmaKqibwllBpQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="323" height="204" style="width: 323px; height: 204px;"/></span></p>